'''埃塞俄比亞－印度關係'''，是指[[印度共和國|印度共和國]]和[[埃塞俄比亞聯邦民主共和國|埃塞俄比亞聯邦民主共和國]]之間的雙邊關係。於1948年7月，印度和埃塞俄比亞建交，在對方國家互設[[使館|使館]]；四年後，兩國的關係提高到大使級<ref name="mfa.gov.et">{{cite web |url=http://www.mfa.gov.et/BilateralMore.php?pg=18 |title=Ministry of Foreign Affairs - MoFA |publisher=Mfa.gov.et |date= |accessdate=2013-02-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715023223/http://www.mfa.gov.et/BilateralMore.php?pg=18 |archivedate=2014-07-15 }}</ref>。印度在衣索比亞首都[[阿迪斯阿貝巴|阿迪斯阿貝巴]]設[[大使館|大使館]]，埃塞俄比亞亦於[[新德里|新德里]]設有大使館。兩國關係密切而友好，印度支持埃塞俄比亞的發展，埃塞俄比亞亦一直支持印度成為[[聯合國安理會常任理事國|聯合國安理會常任理事國]]<ref name="articles.timesofindia.indiatimes">{{cite news|title=Former Ethiopia PM Meles Zenawi helped extend India's footprint in Africa|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-08-22/india/33321909_1_india-africa-indian-companies-india-and-china|accessdate=17 January 2013|newspaper=Times of India|date=August 22, 2012|archive-date=2013-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131211151157/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-08-22/india/33321909_1_india-africa-indian-companies-india-and-china|dead-url=no}}</ref>。印度和埃塞俄比亞兩國在一些國際議題上維持合作關係，如打擊[[恐怖主義|恐怖主義]]、[[聯合國改革|聯合國改革]]、對抗[[氣候變化|氣候變化]]等<ref name="mfa.gov.et" />。

== 經貿關係 ==
於2011-12年，印度和埃塞俄比亞兩國之間的雙邊貿易總額為6.6億[[美元|美元]]，預計於2015年將上升至100億<ref>{{cite news|title='India-Ethiopia relations second to none'|url=http://www.indiaafricaconnect.in/index.php?param=news/4478/africa-in-india/118|accessdate=17 January 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520084229/http://www.indiaafricaconnect.in/index.php?param=news%2F4478%2Fafrica-in-india%2F118|archive-date=2019-05-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。印度出口到埃塞俄比亞的產品包括[[藥物|藥物]]、[[鋼鐵|鋼鐵]]、[[機械|機械]]、[[食品|食品]]、[[塑料|塑料]]、[[油氈產品|油氈產品]]、[[紙|紙]]、[[紡織品|紡織品]]、化工產品和運輸設備鋼鐵等，而埃塞俄比亞出口到印度的產品則包括[[生皮|生皮]]、[[豆類|豆類]]、[[香料|香料]]、[[皮革|皮革]]和[[金屬廢料|金屬廢料]]<ref>{{cite web|title=India-Ethiopia Commercial Bilateral Relations|url=http://www.indianembassy.gov.et/?q=commercial|publisher=The Embassy of India Addis Ababa, Ethiopia|accessdate=17 January 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130316141545/http://www.indianembassy.gov.et/?q=commercial|archivedate=2013年3月16日}}</ref>。印度在埃塞俄比亞的投資額度約為500億美元，是埃塞俄比亞第二大外國投資者；印度於2011年在埃塞俄比亞的投資總額為47.8億美元，並預計會於2015年上升至100億美元<ref>{{cite news|title=Orderly transition in Ethiopia, business ties with India to grow : Envoy|url=http://in.news.yahoo.com/orderly-transition-ethiopia-business-ties-india-grow-envoy-032817854--finance.html|accessdate=17 January 2013|newspaper=Yahoo News|date=30 August 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121011011029/http://in.news.yahoo.com/orderly-transition-ethiopia-business-ties-india-grow-envoy-032817854--finance.html|archive-date=2012-10-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=India approves $4.78 bn investment in Ethiopia|url=http://www.indianexpress.com/news/india-approves--4.78-bn-investment-in-ethiopia/794012|accessdate=17 January 2013|newspaper=Indian Express|date=May 22, 2011}}</ref>。

兩國在2007年簽署了促進和保護雙邊投資協定，又於2011年簽署[[租稅協定|租稅協定]]，以促進兩國之間相互貿易和投資<ref>{{cite news|title=India, Ethiopia to sign BIPPA on Thursday|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2007-07-04/international-business/27952251_1_bippa-seyoum-mesfin-addis-ababa|accessdate=17 January 2013|newspaper=The Times of India|date=July 4, 2007|archive-date=2013-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130929055815/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2007-07-04/international-business/27952251_1_bippa-seyoum-mesfin-addis-ababa|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=India signs pact with Ethiopia to avoid double taxation|url=http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/industry-and-economy/india-signs-pact-with-ethiopia-to-avoid-double-taxation/article2054911.ece|accessdate=17 January 2013|newspaper=The Hindu Businessline|date=27 May 2011}}</ref>。在第二屆{{link-en|印度－非洲論壇峰會|India–Africa Forum Summit}}上，[[印度總理|印度總理]][[曼莫漢·辛格|曼莫漢·辛格]]宣布提高借貸予埃塞俄比亚的[[信用額度|信用額度]]至3億美元，以幫助重建{{link-en|埃塞俄比亞鐵路系統|Rail transport in Ethiopia|阿迪斯阿貝巴－吉布地鐵路}}<ref name="thehindu_a">{{cite news|title=Come and farm our virgin lands, Ethiopia tells India|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/article2048964.ece|accessdate=17 January 2013|newspaper=The Hindu|date=May 26, 2011|archive-date=2011-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110828203319/http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/article2048964.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>；印度其後又提高信用額度至7.1億美元，協助埃塞俄比亞的[[農村電氣化|農村電氣化]]和[[製糖業|製糖業]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Ethiopia seeks investments from India|url=http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/industry-and-economy/economy/article2845322.ece|accessdate=17 January 2013|newspaper=The Hindu Businessline|date=30 January 2012|archive-date=2012-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120703141257/http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/industry-and-economy/economy/article2845322.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 科技合作 ==
印度同意在肉類和奶製品行業的發展上與埃塞俄比亞合作<ref>{{cite news|title=India, Ethiopia to work closely on agri research|url=http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/industry-and-economy/agri-biz/india-ethiopia-to-work-closely-on-agri-research/article2714165.ece|accessdate=17 January 2013|newspaper=Hindu Businessline|date=14 December 2011}}</ref>。為了建立人力資源，印度設立了{{link-en|印度技術和經濟合作計劃|Indian Technical and Economic Cooperation Programme}}，培訓埃塞俄比亞的外交和貿易談判代表<ref name="thehindu_a" />。[[印度陸軍|印度陸軍]]又參與協助培訓和發展[[埃塞俄比亞國民自衛軍|埃塞俄比亞陸軍]]<ref name="articles.timesofindia.indiatimes" />。印度亦承諾於2007年在埃塞俄比亞設立{{link-en|泛非洲電子網絡項目|Pan-African e-Network project}}的第一個試點<ref>{{cite news|title=Africa: Pan African e- Network: a model of "South- South cooperation"|url=http://www.pambazuka.org/en/category/media/55920|accessdate=17 January 2013|newspaper=Pambazuka News|date=24 April 2009|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714220207/http://www.pambazuka.org/en/category/media/55920|archivedate=2014年7月14日}}</ref>。

